mediabox (0.93) unstable; urgency=low

  * Highly improved media scanner for quick scanning and quick startup.

  * Support for various ID3 tag versions (v1, v2.2, v2.3, v2.4).
  
  * Support for album art embedded in ID3 tags.
  
  * High-performant GDK-based rendering engine for a responsive UI and
  more transition effects.
  
  * Buttons for skipping and zooming in the image viewer.
  
  * Enhancements in the default theme.
  
  * Application icon now has the proper size on OS 2008.
  
  * Bugfixes
  
 -- Martin Grimme <martin.grimme@lintegra.de>  Mon, 23 Jan 2008 19:13:00 +0100

